# mdpd correctness test (Step 4: pair_mdpd_omp verification)
# atom_style mdpd provides the per-atom rho array required by pair_style
# mdpd; rho is set to a uniform nonzero value via "set ... sph/rho" (the
# underlying atom->rho array is shared with atom_style sph), since no
# density-summation fix is needed to exercise the ported force formula.
# cut_r (1.5) < cut (2.0) so both the B_rep*wc_r branch (1st neighbor
# shell, r~1.19) and the wc_r=0 clamp (2nd shell, r~1.68) are exercised.
# comm_modify vel yes is required (pair mdpd needs ghost atom velocities).

units           lj
atom_style      mdpd
comm_modify     vel yes

lattice         fcc 0.8442
Lattice spacing in x,y,z = 1.6795962 1.6795962 1.6795962
region          box block 0 6 0 6 0 6
create_box      1 box
