  1 by 1 by 1 MPI processor grid
create_atoms    1 box
Created 864 atoms
  using lattice units in orthogonal box = (0 0 0) to (10.077577 10.077577 10.077577)
  create_atoms CPU = 0.000 seconds
mass            1 1.0

set             group all sph/rho 1.0
Setting atom values ...
  864 settings made for sph/rho

velocity        all create 1.0 12345 loop geom

pair_style      mdpd 1.0 2.0 98765
pair_coeff      * * -40.0 25.0 18.0 2.0 1.5

neighbor        0.3 bin
neigh_modify    every 20 delay 0 check no

fix             1 all nve

thermo          10
run             50

